name: precallauth
description: This repository serves as a template for our end-to-end agent-assisted pipeline. Teams can use this template to: - Brainstorm new software product ideas with a chat LLM. - Convert ideas into detailed software specifications (`spec.md`). - Generate prompt plans (`prompt_plan.md`) and to-do lists (`todo.md`) for execution. - Seamlessly create GitHub issues, manage tasks, and execute work through coding agents.
